I know that the next ship-spec manual is coming, but the capacity of the C11s Hangars in sage would greatly impact decisions going forward. I have been thinking a lot about the Fleet-size points in SAGE, and how smaller ships takes up a great amount of space compared to bigger ships. I'm sure that the team have been thinking through this extensively and that it all will make perfect sense in the end. 
@Deleted User, listening through the Metaverse Nomads episode on the Sage Manual you mentioned that ships with Hangars would have/bring extra Fleet-size points to the Fleet, would they be aligned with the blueprint of the C11? Could you maybe expand on the thinking through this topic, if possible?
Tank you
